@baseUrl = http://localhost:5500
@studentToken = <pegar_token_de_sesion_clerk_del_estudiante>

### Registrar información personal (primera vez)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/students/me/onboarding/personal-info
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "+34600111222",
  "birthday": "1995-03-15",
  "gender": "FEMALE",
  "observations": "Prefiero entrenar por las mañanas",
  "medicalCondition": null
}

### Actualizar información personal
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/students/me/onboarding/personal-info
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "+34600999888",
  "observations": "Actualizado desde el perfil"
}

### Obtener información personal
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/students/me/onboarding/personal-info
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}
